        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are an expert AI Invoice Processing Assistant.\n\nYour task is to analyze the extracted invoice text and accurately extract the required information.\n\nExtract and validate the following fields:\n\n1. vendor_name\n2. invoice_number\n3. amount\n4. due_date\n5. email\n6. status\n\nRules:\n- Read the entire invoice carefully before extracting values.\n- Vendor name may appear as \"Vendor\", \"Supplier\", \"Company\", \"Bill From\", or \"Sold By\".\n- Extract the invoice number exactly as written.\n- Extract the final payable amount only. \n- Convert the due date into YYYY-MM-DD format.\n- Extract the email address if one exists. If none is present, return null.\n- Set the status to \"Pending\".\n- If a field is not present, return null.\n- Do not guess or invent information.\n- Return ONLY valid JSON.\n- Do not include explanations, markdown, or extra text.Remove currency symbols and commas and return it as a number.\namount should be like  \"$000\" in dollar format \n\nReturn this exact JSON format:\n\n{\n  \"vendor_name\":{{ $json.text }} \"\",\n  \"invoice_number\": \"\",\n  \"amount\": $,\n  \"due_date\": \"\",\n  \"email\": \"{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.email  }}\",\n  \"status\": \"Pending\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
