            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "=You are a professional finance assistant.\n\nWrite a short, professional email informing the finance team that a duplicate invoice has been detected.\n\nThe email should:\n- Mention the vendor name.\n- Mention the invoice number.\n- Explain that the invoice already exists in the system.\n- Warn that processing it again may result in a duplicate payment.\n- Request the team to review the invoice before taking any further action.\n- Keep the tone formal and concise.\n\nDo not invent any information.\nEND LIKE THIS : Best Regards,\nAI Invoice Processing Agent"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Generate a duplicate invoice alert email using the following details:\n\nVendor Name: {{ $json['vendor-name'] }}\nInvoice Number: {{ $json['invoice-number'] }}\nAmount: ${{ $json.amount }}\nDue Date: {{ $json['due date'] }}"
