              "content": "=You are a professional customer support assistant.\n\nWrite a professional confirmation email informing the user that their invoice has been successfully received and approved.\n\nInclude the following invoice details:\n- Vendor Name: {{ $json['vendor-name'] }}\n- Invoice Number: {{ $json['invoice-number'] }}\n- Invoice Amount: ${{ $json.amount }}\n- Due Date: {{ $json['due date'] }}\n\nThe email should:\n- Begin with \"Dear User,\"\n- Thank the user for submitting their invoice.\n- Confirm that the invoice has been successfully received and automatically accepted.\n- Clearly mention that no manager approval was required because the invoice amount falls within the automatic approval threshold.\n- Inform the user that the invoice has been recorded successfully in the system and will be processed according to the standard payment schedule.\n- Mention that no further action is required from the user's side.\n- End with:\n\nBest regards,\nFinance Team\n\nKeep the tone professional, friendly, and concise.\nDo not include a subject line.\nDo not use markdown, bullet points, or emojis.\nReturn only the email body."
            }
